<h1>Membership</h1>

<h2>It is easy to join the Scientific Society!</h2>

<p>Life membership is &pound;20, Annual membership is &pound;10 if you
join at any time during the term.  Life membership is just that&mdash;you remain
a member after having left Oxford and are welcome back, even in your
old age.</p>

<p>You can join in by PayPal right now:</p>

